FBIS3-41636 "jpten004___94106" JPRS-TEN-94-004 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Environmental Issues 17 February 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA UKRAINE Toxic Waste in Ukraine Environment Minister Claims Imported Toxic Waste Could Poison All Life AU1911112693 Kiev URYADOVYY KURYER in Ukrainian 16 Nov 93 p 1 AU1911112693 Kiev URYADOVYY KURYER Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report] [Text] Approximately 700 tonnes of toxic waste consisting of first-category chemical substances that could poison all living organisms have already been brought to Ukraine through all sorts of illegal channels, says Yuriy Kostenko, minister of environmental protection. In his opinion, the main reason for the illegal transportation of the deadly cargo is the absence of law that would regulate the procedure for bringing toxic substances to our territory.
